    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2018-04-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2019-09-03T19:18:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>VA Hiring Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill negates enforcement of a noncompete agreement that an applicant for a physician's position in the Veterans Health Administration (VHA) has entered into with a non-Department of Veterans Affairs facility, entity, or individual. As a condition of terminating the noncompete agreement, the physician agrees to serve at the VHA for one year or until the expiration of the non-compete agreement. <br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>VA Hiring Enhancement Act</title>
